node.text: Before sag season over i have to tell my bestie happy birthday... the gifts is a token of love and a celebration of our glow up! We really got it out the mud together! You make it so fun to buy you these beautiful expensive gifts bc u deserve it! You make it so easy to treat u like royal bc you’re so loyal!!! Real friendships isn’t based off what u buy for each other but how u motivate each other, uplift each other and be there for one another in the times that matters the most! I knew we would b Bestfriends/Bossfriends forever when i met you in church 16years ago! I’m so grateful for you @envyme_kendrap  o and @payroll_giovanni didn’t play he started the #cartiparty with that mf watch!!!!! 💎 i love you Kendra
